r-architecture assembly macro definitions\n- `test_lib.c` -- shared library loaded by the test (compiled to test_lib.so)\n- `test_loader.c` -- test harness that validates loader functionality\n- Adding a new architecture requires only: `arch/newarch.h` + relocation case\n  in loader.c + machine check in loader.c. Makefile auto-discovers via wildcard.\n",
